```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

Okay, I am still at (50, 100) and I am not holding the ball. I tried to pick it up twice but failed. I will broadcast to ask for help.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial10_robot2: I am at (50, 100) and failed to pick up the red ball. Can someone help?" }
]
```

I have been waiting for a long time, and I am still not holding the ball. It seems that I cannot pick up the ball no matter what I do. Maybe there is something wrong with my gripper. I will broadcast to ask other robots to pick up the ball.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial10_robot2: I am at (50, 110) and cannot pick up the red ball. Can someone else try to pick it up?" }
]
```

